        <span class="member">Lord Hanningfield</span> moved Amendment No. 176:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0649P0-03191'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0649P0_20030617_GCR_71' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
