        <span class="member">Baroness Maddock</span> moved Amendment No. 178A:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0649P0-03233'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0649P0_20030617_GCR_114' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
